DR ALIYA ADAMU AHMAD

Dr Aliya Adamu Ahmad na daya daga cikin matasan mata manazarta a Nazarin Hausa.
Ta samu digirinta na farko da na biyu daga Jamiʼar Usmanu Danfodiyo Sokoto.
Ta kuma samu digirinta na uku daga Jamiʼar Bayero ta Kano.
Ta koyar a Shehu Shagari College of Education Sokoto.
A halin yanzu tana koyarwa a Sokoto State University, kuma ita ce shugabar Sashen Koyar da Harsunan Nijeriya.
Taken aikin digirinta na uku shi ne: “Rupert Moultrie East: Gudummuwarsa ga Adabin Hausa, da Kuma Sharhi Kan Ayyukansa”.
Ta kuma gabatar da makalu a tarrurruka da dama.
An kuma buga wasu takardunta a mujallun ilmi da littattafai.
A shekarar 2012 ta je SOAS ta Jamiʼar London inda ta yi zaman bicike a matsayin Leventis scholar .
Tana da aure da yaro.

